import React from 'react'
import { Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

import './NewSandBox.css'
import NewsRouter from '../../components/sandbox/NewsRouter'

const { Content } = Layout;

export default function NewsSandBox() {
    return (
        <Layout>

        </Layout>

}
